item.title: Computer
item.description: Each time I start up my laptop it greets me with this message: error: ../../grub-core/commands/search.c:315:no such device: /EFI/custom/apple_set_os.efi. error: ../../grub-core/fs/fshelp.c:257:file ‘/EFI/custom/apple_set_os.efi’ not found. error: ../../grub-core/commands/boot.c:196:you need to load the kernel first. A hacker is also a vandal1 What’s the Use, Sara Ahmed (2019), p.225 ↩︎
